Author: drugstore-diet
Text: Thank you ❤️ This is my first time in treatment and I’m feeling like I’m making this huge mistake you know? I guess I just need to try to be more open to it.

Author: glokash
Text: I’ve been where you are with these thoughts but unfortunately, this shit doesn’t just work itself out. I’ve been back and forth in treatment and what I’ve learned is that it takes a lot of effort and it definitely won’t be effective if you’re not ready/willing to put in that effort. I hope you get to a better place with this, wishing you all the best 💗
